{"bangumi":{"date":"2014-10-03","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/17/6e/88741_a6c52.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/17/6e/88741_a6c52.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/17/6e/88741_a6c52.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/17/6e/88741_a6c52.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/17/6e/88741_a6c52.jpg"},"summary":"　　讲述了国王身边的人投奔了大规模的“狩猎魔女”，并将有着守护之命的魔戒骑士和魔戒法师们杀害。其中的一个魔戒法师，在被处以火刑的当口产下了一个孩子，那是继承了黄金骑士血脉的后代。身为魔戒骑士的父亲救下了这个孩子——莱昂·刘易斯。随着他成长为一个少年，他也承接下了黄金之铠甲。如今国家的实权掌握在了国王身边的恶人手里，而身为国王的父亲重病在床，王子阿方索同母亲一起被赶了出来。为了重夺王权，拯救苍生，王子开始了搜寻传说中的黄金骑士的旅途。莱昂与阿方索，围绕着两个少年的故事就此展开。 ","name":"牙狼〈GARO〉-炎の刻印-","name_cn":"牙狼 炎之刻印","tags":[{"name":"2014年10月","count":157,"total_cont":0},{"name":"MAPPA","count":141,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":122,"total_cont":0},{"name":"特摄改","count":118,"total_cont":0},{"name":"牙狼","count":105,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":66,"total_cont":0},{"name":"小林靖子","count":65,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2014","count":65,"total_cont":0},{"name":"特摄改编","count":39,"total_cont":0},{"name":"热血","count":39,"total_cont":0},{"name":"战斗","count":33,"total_cont":0},{"name":"林祐一郎","count":29,"total_cont":0},{"name":"雨宫庆太","count":22,"total_cont":0},{"name":"奇幻","count":20,"total_cont":0},{"name":"MoNACA","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"特摄","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"雨宮慶太","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2014年","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"東北新社","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"影视改","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TVA","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"野村胜人","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"朴璐美","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"村井贞之","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"橋本和幸","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"10月","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"菅野利之","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"久保宗一郎","count":2,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"牙狼 炎之刻印"},{"key":"